tilizing VR\nVisualize the learning situation of the entire organization, by utilizing VR\nYou can see the degree of understanding, the effect of improving grades, and the degree of contribution.", "short_description": "New medical education platform \"Holoeyes Edu\" by VR\n\n<Three features of Holoeyes Edu>\n1. Understanding human anatomy, techniques, and techniques in 3D space with VR\n2. Anyone can create original VR teaching materials by recording the movement and voice of 3D model data in a three-dimensional space.\n3. User's learning behavior history can be acquired Visualize the effect on understanding and grades by utilizing VR"}]}, "developer_name": "Holoeyes", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://edu.holoeyes.jp/pp", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://edu.holoeyes.jp/tos", "publisher_name": "Holoeyes", "support_website_url": "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScB4YV7GaDs37UWqhnrcvo_fumY0OQaOmK-xP41nC_L6_6Igg/viewform", "website_url": "https://holoeyes.jp/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "393222478507326"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "MEDICINE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "202628509323782"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982498_274814664833748_7958352825385809954_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JCw9rgQBoDIQ7kNvgF5JmoP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=